          { "feature": "comorbidities_or_immunosuppression", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "IV antibiotics: Flucloxacillin 2g Q6H + Benzylpenicillin 1.2g Q6H (or Cefazolin 2g Q8H). If MRSA risk: add Vancomycin or Clindamycin. Elevation. Surgical debridement if necrotizing fasciitis suspected."
